#### What is the BGG Star Realms League?

A [Star Realms](http://www.starrealms.com/) tournament in the form of an ongoing league, with multiple tiers and divisions, that's organized by volunteers on [BoardGameGeek](https://www.boardgamegeek.com).  Find out more about how the league works in the [main announcement thread](https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/1354680/), or go to the [waiting list](https://boardgamegeek.com/thread/1318602/) if you wish to sign up.

- - -

#### What is Star Realms?

A deck-building game by [White Wizard Games](http://www.whitewizardgames.com/) available in both physical (paper) and digital form.  Find out more on the [official Star Realms website](http://www.starrealms.com/).  Neither the BGG Star Realms League nor this website is in any form associated with White Wizard Games, but entirely run by volunteers.
